div.p: １ This class diagram models the Auto-Fix Client written in Angular.
２ Module blocks with yellow background are basic components.
３ Module blocks with orange background are composite components.
４ Module block with red background is layout component.

５ Each component contains a OOOComponent class for Typescript class, a OOOTemplate private inner class for HTML template, and several public static inner classes for declared Typescript data interface.
６ Static members in Typescript classes are hard-coded const values.
７ Methods in HTML template indicates the events invoked by user operations.
